W: I agree. If possible, I’d like to put our money 
towards building schools.  
M: That’s a good idea. Recently, I saw a 
documentary about children who had to study 
in poor conditions.  
W: All right. How much should we give? 
M: Well, I think 500 dollars is the most we can 
afford. We have to consider our budget.  
W: Okay. That leaves us with one option. 
M: Good! This donation will be very meaningful.
